def lsmcli::cmdline::parse_convert_init (   init_id  )  
If init_id is a WWPN, convert it into LSM standard version:
    (?:[0-9a-f]{2}:){7}[0-9a-f]{2}

Return (converted_init_id, lsm_init_type)
